<h1 style="font-size:clamp(28px,5vw,42px);line-height:1.15;margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:800">Top Marketplaces in Ukraine 2026: A Complete Guide for International Brands</h1>

<AuthorByline lang="en" datePublished="2026-04-08" readingTime="14" />
<p style="color:#888;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:24px">Updated: April 2026 &middot; Reading time: 12 min</p>

<img src="/images/blog/top-marketplaces-ukraine-hero.webp" alt="Top marketplaces in Ukraine 2026 — guide for international sellers" style="width:100%;max-height:400px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:32px" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" width="800" height="450">

<p>Ukraine&rsquo;s e-commerce market exceeded $8 billion (200+ billion UAH) in 2025 and continues growing 20-25% annually. For international brands looking to enter this market, local marketplaces offer the fastest path to Ukrainian consumers &mdash; without building your own website or local marketing team.</p>
<p>This guide covers the 7 most important Ukrainian marketplaces, their commission structures (verified April 2026), entry requirements, and &mdash; crucially &mdash; how to handle logistics without establishing a local entity. MTP Group acts as your full-service local partner: warehousing, fulfillment, marketplace integration, payment collection, and returns processing.</p>

