<h2 id="faq" style="margin-top:48px">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
<div style="margin-top:20px">
<details style="border-bottom:1px solid #eee;padding:16px 0"><summary style="font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;list-style:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center">Do I need a Ukrainian legal entity?<span style="color:#e63329;font-size:20px">+</span></summary><p style="margin-top:12px;color:#666"><strong>Not necessarily.</strong> MTP Group acts as your local logistics partner. We handle warehousing, fulfillment, shipping, returns, and payment collection (including cash-on-delivery). For marketplace registration, a local FOP is needed &mdash; we guide you through the process or connect you with local legal partners.</p></details>
<details style="border-bottom:1px solid #eee;padding:16px 0"><summary style="font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;list-style:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center">What is the largest marketplace in Ukraine?<span style="color:#e63329;font-size:20px">+</span></summary><p style="margin-top:12px;color:#666"><strong>Rozetka</strong> &mdash; 30+ million monthly visits, all categories, Ukraine&rsquo;s equivalent of Amazon. Commission 5-27%. Second largest is Prom.ua with 100K+ sellers.</p></details>
<details style="border-bottom:1px solid #eee;padding:16px 0"><summary style="font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;list-style:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center">How much does fulfillment cost in Ukraine?<span style="color:#e63329;font-size:20px">+</span></summary><p style="margin-top:12px;color:#666">From $0.41/order (18 UAH at 200+/day). Storage ~$15/m&sup3;/month. Minimum $114/month. Roughly 50% cheaper than Poland or Germany. <a href="/en/prices/" style="color:#e63329">Full pricing</a>.</p></details>
<details style="border-bottom:1px solid #eee;padding:16px 0"><summary style="font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;list-style:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center">What payment methods do Ukrainians use?<span style="color:#e63329;font-size:20px">+</span></summary><p style="margin-top:12px;color:#666">Cash-on-delivery (COD) accounts for ~60% of orders. Online card payments (Visa/Mastercard) growing. Apple Pay, Google Pay available on major platforms. MTP Group handles COD collection and reconciliation automatically.</p></details>
<details style="border-bottom:1px solid #eee;padding:16px 0"><summary style="font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;list-style:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center">Can MTP Group handle everything for us?<span style="color:#e63329;font-size:20px">+</span></summary><p style="margin-top:12px;color:#666">Yes. We integrate with Rozetka, Prom.ua, Kasta via API. Orders flow automatically into our WMS. We handle: receiving inventory, storage, picking (30 sec/order), packing, shipping via Nova Poshta (4 pickups/day), returns processing, COD payment collection, and Telegram reporting.</p></details>
<details style="border-bottom:1px solid #eee;padding:16px 0"><summary style="font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;list-style:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center">Which marketplace is best for beginners?<span style="color:#e63329;font-size:20px">+</span></summary><p style="margin-top:12px;color:#666"><strong>OLX</strong> &mdash; free start, no registration needed. Perfect for market testing. Then <strong>Kasta</strong> for fashion (~$23 deposit). <strong>Rozetka</strong> for maximum traffic. <strong>Prom</strong> for lowest commissions (from 2.1%).</p></details>
<details style="border-bottom:1px solid #eee;padding:16px 0"><summary style="font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;list-style:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center">Is Ukraine safe for business operations?<span style="color:#e63329;font-size:20px">+</span></summary><p style="margin-top:12px;color:#666">E-commerce in Ukraine has grown 25-30% annually even during the war. MTP Group operates with 3 industrial generators, Starlink internet, and two geographically diversified warehouses. Zero downtime since February 2022. Nova Poshta delivers to 95% of the country.</p></details>
<details style="border-bottom:1px solid #eee;padding:16px 0"><summary style="font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;list-style:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center">How long does delivery take within Ukraine?<span style="color:#e63329;font-size:20px">+</span></summary><p style="margin-top:12px;color:#666">Kyiv &mdash; next day. Major cities &mdash; 1-2 days. Rural areas &mdash; 2-3 days. MTP Group hands packages to Nova Poshta 4 times per day (10:00, 12:00, 15:00, 17:00). Orders placed before 14:00 are shipped the same day.</p></details>
